    "home_page_footer_details_new_dWPAkM": {
      "type": "Home-Page-Footer-Details-New",
      "name": "Home Page Footer Details",
      "settings": {
        "main_background_color": "#FFFFFF",
        "main_heading_text": "",
        "main_information_text": "<!-- footer SEO read more section start -->\n\n<h1>KALKI Fashion - Buy Traditional Indian Clothing and Ethnic Wear Online in India</h1>\n\n<p>Launched in 2007 in Mumbai, KALKI is born out of a fiercely creative spirit and a unique design sensibility. The\n    brand KALKI is synonymous with luxury, traditional Indian craft and a distinct and refreshing design. Representing\n    rooted culture and crafts of India and eclectic fusion through its ethnic wear collection is what explains KALKI’s\n    design philosophy. The clothing fashion brand also has international attention and global appeal to its outfit\n    designs.</p>\n\n<p>Unusual textures, ‘fusion’ of styles, patchworks, ornate embroidery, and gorgeous embellishments on a diverse and\n    vivid colour palette describe the ethnic and designer wear collection of KALKI and give the feeling of ‘going back\n    to the roots. KALKI Fashion is where tradition meets trend—slayin’ ethnic fits with a modern bend! From dreamy\n    lehengas, glam cocktail gowns to menswear mastery, sharp silhouettes, our fashion squad’s got you covered with\n    styles that turn heads. With expert styling and custom designs, we make sure every bride shines.</p>\n\n<h2>Premium And Authentic Wear For Women In India</h2>\n\n<p>21st century women look for clothes that define a major part of their personality. No wonder, they are heavily\n    influenced by the fusion and Indo-western vibes but the love for ethnic wear does prevail in their hearts. As a\n    result, they prefer to go the ‘desi’ way but with a premium and authentic collection that includes premium sarees,\n    designer outfits, fusion lehengas, modern <a href=\"collections/ready-pleated-saree\">ready-to-wear sarees</a> and more. The luxurious\n    collection and the opulent feel of the good clothing not only makes them feel like a queen but also makes a lasting\n    impression at office parties, family gatherings, anniversaries, and weddings.</p>\n\n<h2>The Demand For The Premium & Luxurious Ethnic Attire</h2>\n\n<p>No matter how much a woman loves that comfy pair of jeans; the glory of luxurious ethnic wear is just unmatched and\n    has taken over the minds of ladies once again. Ethnic wear has seen a phenomenal change and quintessential Indian\n    garments like <a href=\"collections/silk-saree\">silk\n        sarees</a>, banarasi suits, and georgette <a href=\"collections/anarkali-suits\">anarkalis</a> are seen as a symbol of grace and\n    tradition. And here are the key features that have helped ethnic fashion clothing from being conventional to a\n    versatile fashion statement.</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>Be it traditional dresses online or ethnic wear for women offline; the premium, high-quality and designer\n            pieces like suits, sarees, palazzo sets, and pre-drapes effortlessly cater to the tastes and preferences of\n            the modern generation.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <p>Influential designers and B-town celebrities have played a pivotal role in re-inventing the image of the\n            Indian traditional dresses for women and designer clothing. Ethnic wear has been made relevant and appealing\n            to the wider audience by infusing or blending contemporary elements into regular or traditional designs.\n            Creative designs like frills, belts, shoulder shrugs, net capes and 3D patches encourage experimentation and\n            exploration of various styles in saree, salwar kameez or <a href=\"collections/designer-lehenga\">designer lehenga choli</a> arena. Prints,\n            patterns, and unconventional fabrics are another area of experimentation.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <p>The visually captivating styles consisting of dramatic dupatta styles, brooches, hangings, bows, billowing\n            sleeves, structured shoulders, floral blazers, and pant outfits are making the latest clothing accessible\n            and appealing to the younger generation who wish to remain connected with their roots and exhibit a unique\n            sense of style and confidence.</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Well, the popularity of <a href=\"collections/bridal-wedding-lehenga\">bridal lehengas</a>, <a href=\"collections/designer-saree\">designer\n        sarees</a>, crafted salwar suits and other ethnic wear is further fuelled by online marketplaces and e-commerce\n    platforms. Whether it is for a special event, for a birthday, to attend a wedding, sangeet or a cocktail; millions\n    around the world are buying ethnic wear online for their global appeal and cultural identity.</p>\n\n\n<h2>Designer Traditional Dress For Men</h2>\n\n<p>The fashion front for men has evolved as greatly as that for women. The <a href=\"/collections/men\">dresses for men online</a> or offline haven’t only outdone the\n    traditional blue and gold for non-glossy textures and matte finish but also the regular and simple kurta or sherwani\n    designs for boho, fusion, formal and Indo-western. Soft pastels like baby pink and mint green, prints like florals,\n    fabrics like net and sheer and elements like trails, frills and pleats are a few of the latest offerings to men’s\n    fashion orbit.</p>\n\n<h2>Trend Check For Men at KALKI</h2>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"collections/sherwanis\">men’s sherwani\n        sets</a>, <a href=\"collections/mens-kurta-set\">kurta sets</a>, <a\n        href=\"collections/indo-westerns-for-men\">Indo-western kurta pyjamas</a>, dhoti kurta sets\n    and traditional dress for men at kalkifashion.com are a sight to behold for powder blush palettes, western vibes,\n    funky tributes and Indian class, culture, and elegance. Angrakha styles and achkan patterns in brocade, velvet, and\n    silk, Jodhpuri sherwanis, close neck kurtas, side-button kurtas and cowl pattern outfits are also available at KALKI\n    to reflect a unique, royal, and period look. Apart from the royal theme; quirky and comfy cotton kurta sets in\n    fusion styles are also a part of KALKI’s traditional wear online. So, be it a Rajput or Mughal-ruler outfit, a\n    simple Indian cotton kurta pyjama for festivals and puja; KALKI has a marvellous range to break the stereotypes.</p>\n\n\n<h2>Designer Kids Wear For Boys & Girls</h2>\n\n<p>The understated appeal for young boys and girls isn’t missing either from KALKI Fashion’s ethnic wear collection.\n    Kid’s dresses like cute cotton lehengas, ethnic gowns, dhoti dresses for boys, kurta pyjama sets, sharara dresses,\n    <a href=\"collections/gown\">Indo-western gowns</a>, salwar\n    kameez, achkan and sherwanis for boys and other cute and comfortable ensembles are available at kalkifashion.com.\n    Affordable yet stylish ethnic options with a cute and celestial appeal and modern twist make the kids ready to grace\n    Indian occasions like weddings and festivals. Colourful and bright clothes, stylish patterns and cute accessories\n    and high-quality fabrics like cotton, silk and linen ensures that the <a href=\"collections/kids\">kid’s ethnic wear</a> and designer silhouette stand out as\n    traditional classics with a stellar twist, instil a rich culture in kids and ensure that they can move or run around\n    comfortably.</p>\n\n<h2>Shop Accessories & Jewellery For Women In India</h2>\n\n<p>Whether it is a gem like emerald worn by royals, a girl’s best friend-diamonds, or ethnic <a\n        href=\"collections/earrings\">earrings</a> in\n    silver or pearls; KALKI Fashion has a stunning range of extravagant <a href=\"collections/jewellery\">jewellery for women</a> of all ages, tastes, and\n    personalities. Multi-stranded <a href=\"collections/necklace\">necklaces</a>, temple jewels, jhumkas, chandelier earrings,\n    <a href=\"collections/maangtikkas\">maangtikka</a>, jhoomer, mathapatti, borla, finger\n    <a href=\"collections/nose-rings-rings\">ring</a>,\n    nath, trendy anklets, and kundan or gold-finish bracelets at KALKI can marvellously be paired with women’s designer\n    sarees, fusion lehengas, gorgeous anarkalis and royal sharara outfits. Pearl or water-drop earrings, fine necklace\n    chains and antique nose pins are also available for those who want something opulent and minimal. Women who are\n    traditional at heart and want that time-tested allure with heavy pieces for their wedding day can look for precious\n    stone and heavy kundan necklace sets at kalkifashion.com. Heavy polki, kundan and meenakari sets in the gold finish\n    are available for that bridal flair.</p>\n\n<h2>Shop All Types Of Traditional Wear Online</h2>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Sarees Online In India</h3>\n        <p>If contemporary sarees with frills, jackets, shrugs and belts are your new-found love; you can conveniently\n            buy sarees online in India at kalkifashion.com. Whether you are modish at heart or want to be in sync with\n            the renewed love of <a href=\"collections/handloom-saree\">handloom</a>, silk, pattu or <a href=\"collections/banarasi-saree\">banarasi sarees</a>; KALKI offers a wide range\n            of options that blend ethnic and western influence seamlessly.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Kurtis Online In India</h3>\n        <p>Kurtis has gained immense popularity and at KALKI, you can find a wide range of variants to explore. Whether\n            you are searching for a <a href=\"collections/yellow-lehenga\">yellow sangeet outfit</a> or quirky mehendi\n            attires; there are a plethora of designs with fashion-friendly details such as undefined hemlines,\n            one-shoulder necklines, tunic patterns, creative kaftans, belted perfections and more to suit your personal\n            style quotient.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Lehengas Online In India</h3>\n        <p>While buying <a href=\"collections/lehenga\">lehengas\n                online</a> at KALKI, you have the freedom to break away from the traditional silhouette rules and\n            explore casual appeal as well. Along with exquisite and heavily embroidered bridal lehengas, KALKI offers a\n            wide range of options including summer-friendly cotton lehengas, glamourous net fabric lehengas, angelic\n            tiered lehengas, modern gown lehengas and <a href=\"collections/lehenga-saree\">Indo-western saree lehengas</a>. KALKI has put\n            in a lot of effort into elevating the creativity and diversity of its ethnic and designer lehenga\n            collection.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Salwar Kameez Online In India</h3>\n        <p>KALKI offers a diverse collection of <a href=\"collections/salwar-kameez\">salwar kameez</a> that cater to various style\n            preferences, ranging from tight-fitted to loose <a href=\"collections/kaftan\">kaftans</a>, Mughal-inspired anarkalis to simple\n            straight looks. The salwar kameez collection features modern modifications such as bell sleeves, belts,\n            shrugs, jackets, side dupattas, off-shoulder neck and more. Whether you prefer widely flared georgette suits\n            or formal <a href=\"collections/cotton-suits\">cotton salwar suits</a>; you have styles\n            available for every occasion including festive events, engagements, and haldi ceremonies. You can also\n            choose from <a href=\"collections/party-wear-suits\">party-wear salwar suits</a> or\n            suits that can be chosen by brides in vivacious and toned-down colours.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Indo-western Dress Online In India</h3>\n        <p><a href=\"collections/dhoti-suits\">Dhoti suits</a>, <a href=\"collections/jumpsuits\">jumpsuits</a>, <a href=\"collections/palazzo-suits\">palazzo suits</a>, salwar kameez with\n            waist belts, lehengas with blazers, suits with net capes, asymmetrical and frilly gowns, <a\n                href=\"collections/co-ord-sets\">co-ord\n                suits</a>, salwar suits without dupatta, pant suits and ready-to-wear sarees are quite in vogue these\n            days. Salwar suits with layers, gatherings, pleats, tassels and panels and other lovely add-ons are\n            interesting picks available at KALKI for edgy and fashionable women.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Sherwani For Grooms & Grooms Online</h3>\n        <p>Sherwanis with a Jodhpuri touch, sherwani sets for groom with pleats, floral prints, high-low hemline and\n            sherwanis with a side panel and Indo-western feel are growing in demand for grooms wear online and offline.\n            Achkan jacket sherwani, sequined sherwani, sherwani with dupatta, cut-dana sherwani and geometric motif\n            sherwani are quite a rage among <a href=\"collections/groom\">Indian grooms</a> and <a href=\"collections/groomsman\">groomsmen</a>.</p>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n        <h3>Buy Wedding Dresses Online</h3>\n        <p>KALKI offers a wide range of ethnic silhouettes for women including wedding silk sarees, salwar kameez,\n            sharara, gharara, Rajasthani lehengas, and gharchola sarees.</p>\n\n        <p>For men, you can choose from a diverse selection of ethnic attire including royal sherwani, achkan style\n            kurta, sherwani set and designer dress for men at kalkifashion.com</p>\n\n        <p>You can also buy kids dresses online, KALKI offers a delightful collection of attire for little ones, ranging\n            from girls dresses cotton salwar kameez, and bright cotton lehengas to boys wear like Indo-western kurta\n            pyjama with dupatta, Nehru jacket kurta set in cotton and bandi jacket set.\n\n        </p>\n\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- footer SEO read more section close -->"
